{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund councils to subsidise more mobility items for disabled and older people",
        "additional_details": "We think too many people are stuck at home, unable to get to the shops, doctors, or see loved ones because they can\u2019t afford a mobility scooter. It\u2019s heart-breaking and unfair. With better access, people could stay independent, connected, and live with dignity \u2014 not isolation.",
        "background": "We want the Government to make mobility scooters and powered wheelchairs more affordable for disabled and elderly people by providing funding for more subsidies. Everyone deserves the freedom to move and live independently.",
